name: Jabsuka
description:
Help Jabsuka on his quest to collect all three ultimate relics of coolness.

Jabsuka is simple but difficult precision platformer. This game will put your platforming skills on test. So, do not worry. You are not the only one struggling. Good luck and happy suffering.

Controls

AD/Horizontal arrows =  Move

Space/Up arrow /W = Jump

F = fps counter (Kinda broken)

M = Mute
